",\"web stuff\",,,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
"</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<कम्प्यूटरनिर्गम>\n"
"\"क्डे\",,,,,०.००,०.००,६.८८,९.८३\n"
",\"ktimetracker\",,,,६.८८,८.७०,६.८८,९.८३\n"
",,\"3.2 विशेषता योजना\",,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",,\"दोषाः\",,,0.00,1.13,0.00,1.13\n"
",,\"परिवर्तनं जाँच - अनुवादमालानि\",,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",,\"समय कार्ड रिपोर्ट\",,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",\"कोपेटे\",,,,०.००,०.००,०.००,०.००\n"
",\"प्रोमो\",,,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
",\"जालसामग्री\",,,,0.00,0.00,0.00,0.00\n"
"</computeroutput> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Top-level tasks are output in the first column, sub-tasks in the second, and "
"so on. The time data is output after the maximum task depth (five in this "
"example). The first time column is <guilabel>Session Time</guilabel>, the "
"second is <guilabel>Time</guilabel>, the third is <guilabel>Total Session "
"Time</guilabel> and the fourth is the <guilabel>Total Time</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"प्रथमस्तम्भे शीर्षस्तरीयकार्यं, द्वितीयस्तम्भे उपकार्यं इत्यादीनि आउटपुट् भवन्ति । "
"अधिकतमकार्यगहनतायाः (अस्मिन् उदाहरणे पञ्च) अनन्तरं समयदत्तांशः निर्गम्यते । प्रथमसमयस्तम्भः "
"<guilabel>सत्रसमय</guilabel>, द्वितीयः <guilabel>समय</guilabel>, तृतीयः "
"<guilabel>कुलसत्रसमय</guilabel> चतुर्थः च <guilabel>कुलसमयः </guilabel> इति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export History to CSV"
msgstr "इतिहासं CSV मध्ये निर्यातयन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To export task history, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Export</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Export...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> and &ktimetracker; displays the same export dialog as shown "
"above. Select option <guibutton>History as CSV</guibutton> in group "
"<guilabel>Report Type</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"कार्य-इतिहासस्य निर्यातार्थं <menuchoice> <guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>निर्यात</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>निर्यात...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> तथा &ktimetracker; उपरि दर्शितवत् निर्यातसंवादं प्रदर्शयति । "
"<guilabel>रिपोर्टप्रकारः</guilabel> इति समूहे <guibutton>CSV इति इतिहासः</"
"guibutton> इति विकल्पं चिनोतु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a date range that you want the task history to cover. Modify the "
"dialog defaults if necessary. You can preview the CSV output on the right "
"side of the dialog. Click <guibutton>Save As...</guibutton> and "
"&ktimetracker; exports the totals for all tasks to the file you enter in a "
"file dialog."
msgstr ""
"एकं तिथिपरिधिं चिनोतु यत् भवान् इच्छति यत् कार्य-इतिहासः आच्छादयतु । आवश्यकतानुसारं "
"संवादपूर्वनिर्धारितं परिवर्तयन्तु । संवादस्य दक्षिणभागे CSV आउटपुट् पूर्वावलोकनं कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति "
"। <guibutton>यथा रक्षतु...</guibutton> तथा &ktimetracker; सञ्चिकासंवादे भवता "
"प्रविष्टायाः सञ्चिकायां सर्वेषां कार्याणां कुलम् निर्यातयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is an example of the output format:"
msgstr "अत्र आउटपुट् प्रारूपस्य उदाहरणम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: literallayout
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<computeroutput>\n"
"Task History\n"
"From Tuesday 06 July 2004 to Tuesday 13 July 2004\n"
"Printed on: 2004-07-13 18:10\n"
"2004-07-06,2004-07-07,2004-07-08,2004-07-09,2004-07-10,2004-07-11,2004-07-12,2004-07-13,\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,\"kde\"\n"
",,1.77,3.23,1.73,,1.37,0.82,8.95,,\"ktimetracker\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"3.2 feature plan\"\n"
",1.13,,,,,,,1.13,,,\"bugs\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"checkin changes - translation strings\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"time card report\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"kopete\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"promo\"\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"web stuff\"\n"
"</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<कम्प्यूटरनिर्गम>\n"
"कार्य इतिहास\n"
"२००४ तमस्य वर्षस्य जुलै-मासस्य ०६ दिनाङ्कस्य मंगलवासरात् २००४ तमस्य वर्षस्य जुलै-मासस्य १३ "
"दिनाङ्कपर्यन्तं मंगलवासरपर्यन्तं\n"
"मुद्रितम्: 2004-07-13 18:10\n"
"२००४-०७-०६,२००४-०७-०७,२००४-०७-०८,२००४-०७-०९,२००४-०७-१०,२००४-०७-११,२००४-०७-१२,२००४-०७-१३,\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,\"क्दे\"।\n"
",,१.७७,३.२३,१.७३,,१.३७,०.८२,८.९५,,\"ktimetracker\" इति ।\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"3.2 विशेषता योजना\"\n"
",१.१३,,,,,,,१.१३,,,\"बग्स्\" ।\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"परिवर्तनं जाँच - अनुवाद ताराः\"।\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,,\"समय कार्ड रिपोर्ट\"।\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"कोपेते\"।\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"प्रोमो\"।\n"
",,,,,,,,0.00,,\"जालसामग्री\"।\n"
"</computeroutput> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first three lines identify when the report was generated and for which "
"date range. The fourth row is a comma-delimited list of the dates in the "
"date range, in ISO 8601 format (YYYY-MM-DD). All subsequent rows list the "
"time logged against each task. The last numeric column is the row total "
"across all days. The task name prints after the total column, and is "
"indented to indicate the task/sub-task relationship. Top level task names "
"appear in the first column after the total."
msgstr ""
"प्रथमत्रयपङ्क्तयः कदा प्रतिवेदनं जनितम्, कस्य तिथिपरिधिः च चिनोति । चतुर्थी पङ्क्तिः "
"तिथिपरिधिस्थानां तिथीनां अल्पविरामेन परिसीमितसूची अस्ति, ISO 8601 प्रारूपेण (YYYY-MM-"
"DD) । अनन्तरं सर्वाणि पङ्क्तयः प्रत्येकं कार्यस्य विरुद्धं लॉग् कृतं समयं सूचीबद्धं कुर्वन्ति । "
"अन्तिमः संख्यात्मकः स्तम्भः सर्वेषु दिनेषु पङ्क्तिसङ्ख्या अस्ति । कार्यनाम कुलस्तम्भस्य अनन्तरं "
"मुद्रयति, कार्य/उपकार्यसम्बन्धं सूचयितुं च इन्डेण्ट् भवति । कुलस्य अनन्तरं प्रथमस्तम्भे "
"शीर्षस्तरीयकार्यनामानि दृश्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &ktimetracker; interface"
msgstr "इति &ktimetracker; अन्तरफलकम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main &ktimetracker; window has the following components: menubar, "
"toolbar, searchbar, task/time window and status bar."
msgstr ""
"मुख्यं &ktimetracker; विण्डो इत्यस्य निम्नलिखितघटकाः सन्ति : मेनूबार, टूलबार, "
"अन्वेषणपट्टिका, कार्य/समयविण्डो तथा स्थितिपट्टिका ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The searchbar is a combined field. As long as you do not press &Enter;, it "
"acts as a filter. Then, only tasks that match your input are shown. As soon "
"as you press &Enter;, your input is used as a name to create a new task."
msgstr ""
"अन्वेषणपट्टिका संयुक्तक्षेत्रम् अस्ति । यावत् भवन्तः &Enter; ततः, केवलं तानि कार्याणि "
"दर्शितानि ये भवतः निवेशेन सह सङ्गतानि सन्ति । &Enter;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>Configuration for PDA</guilabel> in the "
"<guilabel>Appearance</guilabel> page of the settings dialog if you have a "
"touchscreen and your screen real estate is precious. It will disable the "
"search bar and every click will pop up a context menu."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवतः स्पर्शपटलः अस्ति तथा च भवतः पटलस्य अचलसम्पत्त्याः बहुमूल्यः अस्ति चेत् सेटिंग्स् "
"संवादस्य <guilabel>रूपता</guilabel> पृष्ठे <guilabel>PDA कृते विन्यासः</guilabel> इति "
"चिनोतु इदं अन्वेषणपट्टिकां निष्क्रियं करिष्यति तथा च प्रत्येकं क्लिक् सन्दर्भमेनू पॉप् अप करिष्यति "
"।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&ktimetracker; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<स्क्रीनसूचना>&ktimetracker; स्क्रीन</screeninfo> इति"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&ktimetracker; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<वाक्यांश>&ktimetracker; पटल</phrase> इति"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Task/Time window"
msgstr "Task/Time इति विण्डो"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The various tasks are displayed in this window, along with the time "
"accumulated for each in the current session and in total. Tasks being timed "
"have a small clock icon next to the session time."
msgstr ""
"अस्मिन् विण्डो मध्ये विविधानि कार्याणि प्रदर्शितानि सन्ति, वर्तमानसत्रे प्रत्येकस्य कृते "
"सञ्चितसमयेन सह कुलेन च । समयनिर्धारणं क्रियमाणानां कार्याणां सत्रसमयस्य पार्श्वे "
"लघुघटिकाचिह्नं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Subtasks can be created for each task. Clicking the plus sign and minus sign "
"in front of the main task toggles the view of its associated subtasks. The "
"total time accrued for a task includes the times for its subtasks, as well "
"as its own accumulated time."
msgstr ""
"प्रत्येकं कार्यस्य कृते उपकार्यं निर्मातुं शक्यते । मुख्यकार्यस्य पुरतः प्लस् चिह्नं माइनस् चिह्नं च "
"क्लिक् कृत्वा तस्य सम्बद्धानां उपकार्यस्य दृश्यं टॉग्ल् भवति । कार्यस्य कृते सञ्चितस्य कुलसमये तस्य "
"उपकार्यस्य समयाः, तथैव स्वस्य सञ्चितः समयः अपि अन्तर्भवति ।"

