#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid "Glossary"
msgstr "शब्दावली"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>A</title>"
msgstr "<title>एकः</title>"

#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid "active task"
msgstr "सक्रिय कार्यम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:568
#, no-c-format
msgid "A task which has a timer running."
msgstr "एकं कार्यं यस्य समयनिर्धारकः प्रचलति।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>D</title>"
msgstr "<title>घ</title>"

#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid "<glossterm>&DBus;</glossterm>"
msgstr "<glossterm>&DBus;</glossterm> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid "An interprocess communication protocol. Short for Desktop Bus."
msgstr "एकः अन्तरप्रक्रियासञ्चारप्रोटोकॉलः । Desktop Bus इत्यस्य संक्षिप्तम् ।"

#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "desktop"
msgstr "डेस्कटॉप् इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;, FreeBSD and other systems that run X.Org Server have multiple "
"desktops. You can typically have four different desktops installed by "
"default. Each desktop can display its own set of programs and files. When "
"&kde; &plasma; first starts up, the desktop you see is Desktop 1. If you "
"press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>, you "
"will see Desktop 2. Pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F1</"
"keycap></keycombo> will bring back Desktop 1."
msgstr ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;, FreeBSD इत्यादिषु प्रणालीषु ये X.Org Server चालयन्ति तेषु बहुविधाः "
"डेस्कटॉप् सन्ति । सामान्यतया भवन्तः पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण चत्वारि भिन्नानि डेस्कटॉप् संस्थापयितुं "
"शक्नुवन्ति । प्रत्येकं डेस्कटॉप् स्वस्य कार्यक्रमानां सञ्चिकानां च समुच्चयं प्रदर्शयितुं शक्नोति । "
"यदा &kde; &प्लाज्मा; प्रथमं आरभ्यते, भवन्तः यत् डेस्कटॉप् पश्यन्ति तत् Desktop 1. यदि भवान् "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> नुदति तर्हि "
"भवान् Desktop 2 द्रक्ष्यति <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F1</keycap></"
"keycombo> इत्यनेन Desktop 1 पुनः आनयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>H</title>"
msgstr "<title>ह</title>"

#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "history"
msgstr "इतिहास"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &ktimetracker; is configured to log history, it will record every start/"
"stop timer event. This history is not cleared when times are reset and "
"remains on file until the task is deleted."
msgstr ""
"यदि &ktimetracker; इतिहासं लॉग् कर्तुं विन्यस्तं भवति, एतत् प्रत्येकं start/stop timer "
"घटनां अभिलेखयिष्यति । एषः इतिहासः यदा समयाः पुनः सेट् भवन्ति तदा न स्वच्छः भवति तथा च "
"यावत् कार्यं विलोपितं न भवति तावत् सञ्चिकायां तिष्ठति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>S</title>"
msgstr "<title>स</title>"

#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid "session"
msgstr "सत्र"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A user-defined starting point for the session timers. A new session begins "
"when you select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Start New "
"Session</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Session data is not saved when you "
"create a new session."
msgstr ""
"सत्रसमयनिर्धारकाणां कृते उपयोक्तृनिर्धारितः आरम्भबिन्दुः । यदा भवान् <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> <guimenuitem>नवीनसत्रं आरभत</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> इति चिनोति तदा नूतनं सत्रं आरभ्यते । यदा भवन्तः नूतनं सत्रं निर्मान्ति तदा "
"सत्रदत्तांशः न रक्षितः भवति ।"

#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:614
#, no-c-format
msgid "system tray"
msgstr "प्रणाली ट्रे"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:615
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The system tray is in the bar that (by default in &kde; &plasma;) appears at "
"the bottom of the screen. In this system tray <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"systray.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> the &ktimetracker; icon is on the far "
"right."
msgstr ""
"सिस्टम् ट्रे तस्मिन् पट्टिकायां अस्ति यत् (पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण &kde; &plasma; इत्यत्र) "
"स्क्रीनस्य अधः दृश्यते । अस्मिन् सिस्टम् ट्रे <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"systray.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> &ktimetracker; icon अत्यन्तं दक्षिणभागे अस्ति।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>T</title>"
msgstr "<title>टी</title>"

#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid "top level task"
msgstr "शीर्ष स्तरीय कार्य"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid "A task with no parent tasks."
msgstr "मातापितृकार्यं नास्ति इति कार्यम्।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DBus; Interface"
msgstr "&DBus; अन्तरफलकम्"

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>version</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>संस्करण</refentrytitle> इति"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>version</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>संस्करण</refname> इति"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid "Return &ktimetracker;'s version."
msgstr "&ktimetracker;'s संस्करणं प्रत्यागच्छतु ।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid "QString version()"
msgstr "QString संस्करणम् () ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:658 index.docbook:677 index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>version()</function> is a &DBus; call that returns "
"&ktimetracker;'s version number; for example 4.3.1. The version number is "
"returned as a string in the typical &GNU; format of major.minor.bugfix."
msgstr ""
"<function>version()</function> इति &DBus; call यत् &ktimetracker;'s "
"संस्करणसङ्ख्यां प्रत्यागच्छति; यथा ४.३.१. संस्करणसङ्ख्या विशिष्टे &GNU; major.minor.bugfix "
"इत्यस्य प्रारूपम्।"

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>quit</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>निवृत्तं</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>quit</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>निर्गम</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &ktimetracker;'."
msgstr "&ktimetracker;' इति त्यजतु।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "QString quit()"
msgstr "QString quit ()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>quit()</function> is a &DBus; call that provides a way that an "
"external program can gracefully shutdown &ktimetracker;."
msgstr ""
"<function>quit()</function> इति &DBus; आह्वानं यत् एकं मार्गं प्रदाति यत् बाह्यः "
"कार्यक्रमः &ktimetracker;."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>addTask</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>कार्यं योजयतु</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>addTask</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>कार्यं योजयतु</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add new task."
msgstr "नूतनं कार्यं योजयन्तु।"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:728
#, no-c-format
msgid "QString addTask(QString taskname)"
msgstr "QString addTask (QString कार्यनाम) 1.1."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "पैरामीटर्"

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid "taskname"
msgstr "कार्यनाम"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:735
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of new task."
msgstr "नवकार्यस्य नाम ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>addTask(QString taskname)</function> is a &DBus; call that adds a "
"new top-level to-do to the current storage. The UID of the new task is "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"<function>addTask(QString कार्यनाम)</function> इति &DBus; call यत् "
"वर्तमानभण्डारणस्थाने नूतनं शीर्षस्तरीयं कार्यं योजयति । नूतनकार्यस्य UID प्रत्यागच्छति ।"
